Deploy Your Bot:

Once you are satisfied with the bot's setup in the local environment, you can consider deploying it. Botpress supports various deployment options which can be configured in the data/global/botpress.config.json file.
javascript
 
{
  "httpServer": {
    "host": "0.0.0.0",
    "port": 3000,
    "externalUrl": "https://your-deployment-url.com",
    "apiKey": "bp_pat_7Ss7hxPiCV62qvOAwumuvxWEWlpHhYaVomEz"
  }
}
